}

## Import


Database clusters can be imported using the `id` returned from DigitalOcean, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import digitalocean:index/databaseCluster:DatabaseCluster mycluster 245bcfd0-7f31-4ce6-a2bc-475a116cca97
```
